The Eternal Legacy of Sarga 185
Grief became inquiry.
Inquiry found the Guru.
The Guru gave direction.
Practice ripened into realization.
Realization dissolved all doubt.
And when all doubt disappeared, nothing remained except the infinite peace of Brahman.
May this be not merely Kundadanta's story,
but the silent pilgrimage of our own hearts.
